Sentence: Strong staining for bFGF was also found in cardiac muscle fibers, smooth muscle cells of mid - size blood vessels, the gut and the myometrium, in central nervous system neurons and cerebellar Purkinje cells, and on epithelial cells of the bronchi, colon, endometrium, and sweat gland ducts of the skin.
